## quick_task

**Samples:** a=3, b=2; paired epochs=2

> ⚠️ Small sample size (n<5): a=3, b=2. Treat deltas as observed, not statistically supported.

> ⚠️  LOW STATISTICAL POWER: N=2 paired epochs. Minimum recommended: N=5 for exploratory, N=10+ for CI gates.
>     Current power at d=0.5 (medium effect): 11% — 89% chance of missing a real difference.
>     Run with --epochs 10 for reliable conclusions.

